programme.title: Memori: Pengantin Lari
programme.desc: Mira melarikan diri semasa hari perkahwinannya kerana tidak mahu berkahwin dengan lelaki yang meminangnya. Mira telah ke rumah Nita di kuala lumpur. Mira mencari kerja namun tidak sesuai dengannya. Nita membantu Mira mendapatkan kerja di syarikat arman sebagai pembantu peribadi. Mira meletak jawatan kerana mahu pulang ke kampung untuk meminta maaf pada ibu bapanya. Ibu bapa Mira telah memberitahu siapa sebenar bakal suaminya. Mira terkejut kerana orang itu adalah Arman. Mira akhirnya menerima Arman dan mereka berkahwin. Pelakon: Chacha Maembong, Shah Iskandar, dan Sura Sojangi.

programme.desc: Zaman dan Erina di amanahkan menjaga zuriat dari penjara. Zuriat itu adalah dari isteri pertamanya Shara yang di penjarakan kerana kesalahan mengedar dadah. Dalam episod ini Zaman selalu balik kerja lewat kerana membuat penghantaran. Shara turut diganggu ahlong semasa di kafe. Zaman telah memberi Shara duit yang banyak untuk membayar hutang ahlong. Setelah Zaman mendapat hasil yang lumayan dengan membuat kerja penghantaran, Shara turut berminat dengan kerja tersebut. programme.title: Panggung RTM : Takkan Terlerai
programme.desc: Ikuti kisah suka dan duka yang mengisahkan pengorbanan seorang abang iaitu Afiq yang menjaga adik istimewa, Irfan yang pekak dan bisu setelah kematian ibu bapa mereka. Irfan dan Afiq berkomunikasi berdua dan orang keliling dengan menggunakan Bahasa Isyarat. Afiq bekerja di kafe dan membuat kerja sambilan melukis serta menjual lukisan bagi menyara kehidupan mereka berdua. Irfan bercita-cita untuk menjadi olahragawan terkenal dan meminati sukan badminton. Afiq duduk menyewa di sebelah rumah wanita berbangsa India yang selalu mengambil berat tentang Afiq dan Irfan. Afiq telah berkenalan secara tidak sengaja yang mencari pelukis mural. Aira juga banyak membantu afiq dalam mengembangkan bakat seni lukisnya. Pelakon: Zahiril Adzim, Mohd Haridz Suhaile, Syarifah Sofia Syed Hussein, Susila Devi dan Penampilan Khas: Yap Leong Chai (Steve Yap).

programme.title: Perang Bibir Ep10
programme.desc: Nabila Huda dan Issey kembali bersaing. Nabila Huda, yang mengetuai kumpulan perempuan, digandingkan bersama Sherry Al-Hadad dan Ramona Zam Zam menentang kumpulan lelaki yang dipimpin oleh Issey yang digandingkan bersama Dennis Yin dan Izzue Islam. Kedua dua kumpulan perlu menari sepadan dengan rentak lagu yang dimainkan. Markah akan diambil kira daripada kekuatan jeritan para penonton. Pertandingan untuk memenangi RM6,000 sememangnya susah kerana peserta juga perlu bersaing di dalam 2 mini games. Markah tertinggi di penghujung rancangan akan menjadi juara untuk episod ini. Kumpulan lelaki yang mengumpul lebih markah telah diistihar sebagai pemenang.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep20
programme.desc: Memaparkan Sheila bersama Nizam yang bersetuju berlakon sebagai suami yang biasa. Sheila memperkenalkan Nizam kepada ibunya yang masih berada di katil hospital. Ibu Sheila terima dengan seadanya. Sementara itu hubungan Hani dan Mizan terus mesra membuatkan Nizam mencemburui. Cemburu Nizam terus menebal apabila Hani mengakui dia telah mengandung kepada keluarganya, walau pun itu satu helah dia bersama Mizan. Mempercayai itu, Nizam telah menghubungi Suraya dan mengugutnya lagi. Dia meminta Suraya melakukan sesuatu asalkan kandungan Hani gugur. Bertindak dari itu, Suraya bertemu Hani dan Mizan yang baru dirawat tangannya. Mizan diminta Hani berada di dalam kereta, semasa inilah sempat Suraya menyiku perut Hani. Mizan yang keluar membantu dihentak dengan beg tangannya berisi batu. Mizan menerima rawatan pesakit luar. Ketika ibu bapa mereka melawat, Nizam turut serta tetapi hanya berpura-pura. Kesempatan itu, Nizam cuba mendekati Hani mendesak dan memujuknya. Hani tetap menolak sambil bertegas dia amat mencintai Mizan. Suraya kini bimbang dia diburu polis. Kebetulan Dato Fuad yang menyimpannya datang. Suraya terus mengadu membuatkan Dato Fuad mengaturkan orang-orangnya untuk menghalang Nizam mengugut Suraya dan memberi ribuan ringgit. Hubungan Nizam dengan Sheila masih dingin dan Nizam mengulangi dia tetap memperisterikan Hani. Setelah berfikir sebak mungkin, Mizan menghubungi ibu dan bapanya memaklumkan Hani keguguran dan tiada masalah.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep36
programme.desc: zgr menjadi marah apabila dia mengetahui bahawa Tolga ialah bos Ezgi. Ezgi segera berhenti. Tetapi Tolga tidak akan selesa sehingga dia mendapat La Gabbia, dia telah pun membuat perancangan untuk meletakkan Ezgi dalam situasi yang sukar dengan sokongan Gizem. Dia mengambil kesempatan daripada kelemahan zgr untuk Ezgi. Apabila bercakap mengenai Ezgi, ia menjadi lebih sukar bagi zgr untuk membuat keputusan menentang kehendak Tolga. Sementara itu, zgr berurusan dengan restoran baharu dan pembukaannya. Terhadap semua kesukaran, perkara yang paling penting bagi zgr dan Ezgi ialah cinta mereka antara satu sama lain. Tetapi Tolga dan Serdar tidak berniat untuk membiarkan mereka bersendirian.

Rasya belum bersedia untuk berjumpa dengan mana-mana lelaki. Rasya takut ekoran rasa panaroid. Rasya teringat lagi semasa mama tinggalkan dirinya.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep16
programme.desc: Memaparkan Shariff terus meminati Hani dia memujuk Yusri untuk menceritakan sejauh mana hal Hani. Dalam masa yang sama Shariff ada masalah keluarga berpunca bapanya. Dia juga akui kepada Dzul dan pernah menghubungi Hani untuk temujanji, tetapi Hani tegas menolak. Nizam yang baru bekerja di Johor Bahru menerima kunjungan mengejut Sheila. Di peringkat mula Nizam bukan sahaja memarahi Sheila tetapi tidak mahu menerima kedatangan dan melayannya. Dia juga mengherdik dengan kata-kata kesat. Sehingga Sheila merayu agar memberi ruang dan peluang akhirnya terbuka juga hati Nizam. Lantaran itu, Sheila berkesempatan memberi tahu secara serius kepada Nizam bahawa Mizan amat sayangkan Hani dan lupakan sahaja hasratnya. Setakat ini Nizam masih tidak percaya. Apa pun dia juga menyatakan kepada Sheila dia akan mencari rumah mereka di Johor Bahru dan meminta Sheila pulang. Mizan delima kerana membayangkan keadaan yang amat tidak sesuai berlaku jika Sharif rakan baiknya menghawini Hani dan mereka pula sepejabat. Dalam pada itu Suraya pula cuba mengapi-apikan rumah tangganya. Antara Mizan dengan Hani masih dingin, tetapi Hani lebih tenang dan masing-masing tidak abaikan tanggungjawab rumah tangga.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep18
programme.desc: Memaparkan semua keluarga Hani ada di rumahnya. Nizam mahu tidak mahu terpaksa menerima Sheila dan anaknya tidur sebilik. Sementara itu hubungan Hani dan Mizan yang mesra seperti bukan berlakon lagi. Dalam pada itu Nizam tetap menyukai Hani dan Hani tahu mengelak dan berbalas cakapnya. Mereka sekeluarga juga ke hospital. Di hospital, hubungan Nizam dan Sheila masih tegang. Nizam berterus terang dia hanya berlakon jika berjumpa dengan ibu Sheila kerana dia akan berkahwin dengan Hani dan Sheila tetap akan diceraikan. Demi untuk nampak tenang, Sheila mengalah, sanggup terima apa yang dihajat Nizam. Walau pun begitu dia meminta masa. Sheila melawat ibunya di wad, walau pun dia berkata-kata telah berkahwin dan memohon maaf tetapi ibunya tidak sedar ketika itu. Sheila juga bersemuka sekali lagi dengan Hani dan terang-terang Hani menafikan segala hasrat Nizam dan didengari Nizam. Sementara itu Shariff tetap menyukai Hani dan meminta bantuan ibu saudaranya Umairah isteri Datuk Fuad menjadi wakilnya agar Hani kelak menjadi isterinya. Dalam masa yang sama Datuk Fuad, suami Umairah curang telah mengamalkan rasuah membolehkan Ah Meng mudah perolehi tender sepatutnya diperolehi syarikat mereka. Semuanya gara-gara Suraya. Berikutan itu Shariff diminta Umairah utamakan menyelamatkan syarikat mereka. Umairah juga memaklumkan Shariff berdasarkan biodata Hani, Hani itu adalah adik kandungnya.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep19
programme.desc: Memaparkan Hani dan Mizan yang semakin mesra berada bersama keluarga mereka di rumah keluarga Sheila. Bapa Sheila masih terlantar dan ibunya masih tidak sedarkan diri di hospital. Hubungan Sheila dengan Nizam masih dingin dan tegang. Mereka sering bertengkar tidak di hadapan ibu dan bapa Nizam. Dalam keadaan begitu semasa perbincangan keluarga, Sheila memberani diri meminta Nizam agar dapat menguruskan segala urusan kerja bapa Sheila yang penting. Ibu dan bapa Nizam serta disokong Mizan menggalak sedemikian. Nizam yang masih ada hati terhadap Hani mencadangkan Hani turut bekerja bersamanya. Hani tidak membuat keputusan, tetapi berhelah kononnya dia mengalami tanda tanda mengandung. Dia bergegas ke bilik air dan dituruti Mizan yang benar benar hendak membantu, langsung mereka hanya berpakat sedemikian. Sementara itu, Shariff yang sering mengingati Hani menghubunginya dan memaklumkan dia terpilih tawaran bekerja. Hani tidak memberi sebarang ketetapan. Sheila diugut Nizam dan meminta bayaran kerana bersetuju berbaik berlakon sebagai suami. Kebetulan ibu Sheila telah sedar dan menerima dengan bersyukur Nizam apabila Sheila memperkenalkan sebagai suaminya. Hani dan Mizan terus mesra dan mereka banyak berkomunikasi dan kedua mereka membeli sedikit barang keperluan untuk menemui Yusri, adik dan atuknya.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep20
programme.desc: Memaparkan Sheila bersama Nizam yang bersetuju berlakon sebagai suami yang biasa. Sheila memperkenalkan Nizam kepada ibunya yang masih berada di katil hospital. Ibu Sheila terima dengan seadanya. Sementara itu hubungan Hani dan Mizan terus mesra membuatkan Nizam mencemburui. Cemburu Nizam terus menebal apabila Hani mengakui dia telah mengandung kepada keluarganya, walau pun itu satu helah dia bersama Mizan. Mempercayai itu, Nizam telah menghubungi Suraya dan mengugutnya lagi. Dia meminta Suraya melakukan sesuatu asalkan kandungan Hani gugur. Bertindak dari itu, Suraya bertemu Hani dan Mizan yang baru dirawat tangannya. Mizan diminta Hani berada di dalam kereta, semasa inilah sempat Suraya menyiku perut Hani. Mizan yang keluar membantu dihentak dengan beg tangannya berisi batu. Mizan menerima rawatan pesakit luar. Ketika ibu bapa mereka melawat, Nizam turut serta tetapi hanya berpura-pura. Kesempatan itu, Nizam cuba mendekati Hani mendesak dan memujuknya. Hani tetap menolak sambil bertegas dia amat mencintai Mizan. Suraya kini bimbang dia diburu polis. Kebetulan Dato Fuad yang menyimpannya datang. Suraya terus mengadu membuatkan Dato Fuad mengaturkan orang-orangnya untuk menghalang Nizam mengugut Suraya dan memberi ribuan ringgit. Hubungan Nizam dengan Sheila masih dingin dan Nizam mengulangi dia tetap memperisterikan Hani. Setelah berfikir sebak mungkin, Mizan menghubungi ibu dan bapanya memaklumkan Hani keguguran dan tiada masalah.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep32
programme.desc: zgr sangat terharu kerana semua yang dia lalui kebelakangan ini dan memutuskan untuk berehat dan pergi ke hutan untuk mengosongkan fikirannya. Tetapi detik damainya di sana tidak bertahan lama, Ezgi, Ozan dan Deniz pergi mencarinya. Mereka semua mempunyai hari yang menyeronokkan bersama. zgr mengambil kekuatannya daripada Ezgi dalam setiap negatif yang dia alami. Setiap saat dia berkongsi dengannya, dia menyedari bahawa dia tidak boleh tanpanya dan melamar Ezgi. Ezgi akhirnya menjalani impiannya, mencari cinta sejati. Dia mengiyakan cadangannya untuk bahagia selamanya dengan zgr.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep33
programme.desc: Selepas semua kekecewaan Ezgi menuju ke Bursa untuk membersihkan kepalanya. Nevin dan nal mempersoalkan keadaan Ezgi ini. Walaupun Ezgi menyembunyikan pengalamannya dengan zgr, semuanya terbongkar apabila zgr datang ke Bursa. Permohonan maaf zgr tidak mengubah apa-apa. zgr tidak mempercayainya, yang menyebabkan dia sangat kecewa. Semakin zgr menyendiri, semakin dia merindui Ezgi dan semakin dia menyedari betapa dia menyayanginya. Keadaan fikiran ini mengaktifkan Ozan. Cansu dan Deniz juga kecewa dan menyesal kerana mereka melayan Ezgi dengan salah. Mereka juga bekerjasama dengan Ozan dan cuba membawa Ezgi dan zgr bersama.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep34
programme.desc: Selepas semua kekecewaan Ezgi menuju ke Bursa untuk membersihkan kepalanya. Nevin dan nal mempersoalkan keadaan Ezgi ini. Walaupun Ezgi menyembunyikan pengalamannya dengan zgr, semuanya terbongkar apabila zgr datang ke Bursa. Semakin zgr menyendiri, semakin dia merindui Ezgi dan semakin dia menyedari betapa dia menyayanginya. Keadaan fikiran ini mengaktifkan Ozan. Cansu dan Deniz juga kecewa dan menyesal kerana mereka melayan Ezgi dengan salah. Mereka juga bekerjasama dengan Ozan dan cuba membawa Ezgi dan zgr bersama.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep35
programme.desc: Ezgi sangat terharu dengan kejutan zgr. Semua kebencian terhadap zgr berlalu. Dalam proses ini, kedua-duanya lebih memahami betapa mereka menghargai satu sama lain. Mereka membuka lembaran baru dalam hubungan mereka, tidak ada lagi tempat untuk pembohongan. Jadi mereka memutuskan untuk memberitahu keluarga mereka bahawa mereka bersama. Nevin menerima perhubungan ini walaupun dia tidak menginginkannya sangat, Sevim pula tidak mahu Ezgi dan zgr bersama. Ezgi mengadakan acara pertamanya di syarikat organisasi yang diupahnya, dan kejutan menantinya di acara ini. Sementara itu, Serdar mengambil tindakan sekali lagi untuk mendapatkan Ezgi, tetapi apabila dia mengetahui bahawa zgr dan Ezgi bersama, dia kecewa dan keadaan ini menjadikannya lebih bercita-cita tinggi.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep36
programme.desc: zgr menjadi marah apabila dia mengetahui bahawa Tolga ialah bos Ezgi. Ezgi segera berhenti. Tetapi Tolga tidak akan selesa sehingga dia mendapat La Gabbia, dia telah pun membuat perancangan untuk meletakkan Ezgi dalam situasi yang sukar dengan sokongan Gizem. Dia mengambil kesempatan daripada kelemahan zgr untuk Ezgi. Apabila bercakap mengenai Ezgi, ia menjadi lebih sukar bagi zgr untuk membuat keputusan menentang kehendak Tolga. Sementara itu, zgr berurusan dengan restoran baharu dan pembukaannya. Terhadap semua kesukaran, perkara yang paling penting bagi zgr dan Ezgi ialah cinta mereka antara satu sama lain. Tetapi Tolga dan Serdar tidak berniat untuk membiarkan mereka bersendirian.

programme.desc: Selepas bertemu Serdar di Gcek, Ezgi dan zgr mula berfikir tentang apa yang perlu dilakukan apabila mereka mengetahui bahawa Serdar juga akan menghadiri majlis perkahwinan Ebru. Rakan-rakan mereka cuba mencari idea dan membantu mereka untuk meneruskan perkahwinan. Sementara itu, Sevim dan Nevin bergaul dengan baik, dan dengan bimbingan Fitnat, mereka mula merancang untuk mengatasi Ezgi dan zgr. programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: Happy Enemy(M) Ep3031
programme.desc: Pei-Pei Wu and Yu-Hsuan Lee have been comparing with each other since childhood. They had a crush on each other but later became rivals because of an accident. They both wished each other would disappear from their lives; however, they are neighbors. Pei-Pei and Yu-Hsuan have been fighting, yet they inevitably fell into the destined love with each other. If fighting against each other is a way of communication and caring, then these quarrelsome lovers are getting closer and growing together. When they gradually start to let go of their competitive attitude that is full of hostility, they even start to click with each other!

programme.title: Lion Rock
programme.desc: Based on the true story of David Ki, one of Asias top rock climbers who lost everything when a motorcycle accident crippled him. Rather than succumbing to his fate, David found a way of scaling the dizzying peaks again by becoming a wheelchair-bound athlete and soon reached the peak of Lion Rock!

programme.title: My Kickass Wife
programme.desc: Jade is a beautiful royal guard who is set up for marriage by the Queen in order to avoid the King setting eyes on her. Jade falls for Sean and helps him win the contest for her. After the wedding, Sean discovers her bad temper and visits a brothel in his despair. He meets and is attracted to a girl there, not knowing she has a secret agenda...

programme.title: Love on Delivery
programme.desc: A delivery boy Yin wants to impress his dream girl Li, so he enrols in a martial arts course to learn strange moves. Being timid, Yin saves Li while wearing a Garfield mask but the credit is stolen by Karate Master, Liu. To prove himself and win Li back, Yin defeats Liu in the ring with his unique martial arts move "Invincible Wind and Fire Spin".

programme.title: Red Line
programme.desc: A former professional car racer, Le falls into despair after causing his brother's death in a car race, until he meets female doctor Hui and becomes an ambulance driver who vows to save lives with speed. Meanwhile, the truth about his brothers accident emerges with the investigation of Le's three good friends...

programme.title: Where The Wind Blows
programme.desc: Founded in the 70s, Hong Kongs ICAC is committed to fight corruption in the police force. Detectives Lui Lok and Nam Kong build a corruption system that creates conflicts between the triad and the police. When ICAC hunts down the two, their control finally comes to an end. Where the wind blows, Hong Kong is no longer what it used to be!

programme.title: Adventure of the King
programme.desc: The Ming Emperor Zhengde flees the palace to see the world after his mother orders him to marry an ugly princess. He disguises as a commoner and escapes with his advisors, but a gambling mishap causes them to part ways and Zhengde lost all his money. Phoenix, the owner of Lung Fung Inn, takes him in out of pity, and thus begins his new adventure...

programme.title: Detective Chinatown 3
programme.desc: After the events in Bangkok and New York, Tang Ren and Qin Feng are invited to solve a murder case in Tokyo, but it turns out to be a challenge for the worlds best detectives. While the case has become complicated and confusing since the worlds top detective Q got involved, a hilarious challenge for the best detectives in Asia has just begun

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: First Love the Litter on the Breeze
programme.desc: This movie is the directorial debut of actor Eric Kot for Wong Kar Wai. Eric features the topic of first love in his first movie: a sleepwalker guided through the night by a lonely admirer is bizarre yet romantic, while a married grocer facing the vengeful first love that he once rejected is heartbreaking.

programme.title: Deception of the Novelist
programme.desc: This is a sexy thriller adapted from the hit story by the famous internet author, Xxharuki. A self-help book author Xu lives happily with his wife Jeana and their son. However, when a voluptuous and seductive tenant rents their apartment upstairs, Xus life is turned upside down.

programme.title: Napping Kid
programme.desc: Xiao Rus financial analysis for a bank client was stolen online. A ransom has to be paid within three days or else the document would be disclosed. To protect the clients data, the company brings in the police to investigate. In the meantime, an analyst disappears and the Technical Director resigns. Is there a bigger crisis lurking behind?

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 1
programme.desc: Wu Dang Sects Zhang Chui Shans son, Zhang Wu Ji, finds himself accidentally embroiled in the fight for the Dragon Sabre. When he unwittingly learns the powerful martial arts skills from the Jiuyin scriptures, Wu Ji proceeds to help the Six Major sects fight against the corrupt government.

programme.title: New Police Story
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Wing is an elite in the police force but has been drowning his guilt in booze after his entire team was killed by the Gang of Five in a mission. A year later, a young rookie detective with a complicated background is assigned to partner Wing and manages to inspire him into action, as Wing vows to take down the gang.

programme.title: Look Up
programme.desc: This film celebrates the 25th anniversary of Hong Kongs Handover in a series of four cultural stories about young Hong Kongers from different walks of life: a young man with autism pursuing his dream, a reconciliation between father and son, a Chinese opera star helping young pop singers, and a Nepali youth becoming a professional lion dancer.

programme.title: Cyber Heist
programme.desc: Hackers have caused a large-scale cyber attack, but luckily cyber security engineer Chun, manages to fend it off with his protective firewall system. To Chun's surprise, his boss is the mastermind of the attack, and when Chun gets trapped in a money laundering operation, he must fight against his boss in the cyber world to prove his innocence.

programme.title: Model Family
programme.desc: A single-parent family (Yu Xiang and Tong Tong) move into a new neighbourhood where everyones life seems perfect. However, while things may look rosy on the outside, dark secrets and horror raid each family from the inside, and nothing really are as they seem.

programme.title: The Mad Monk
programme.desc: Stephen Chow plays an arrogant god in Heaven who is being punished for his pranks and mistakes. He is sent to Earth and reincarnate as Mad Monk to change the destiny of three misguided souls - a prostitute, a beggar and a villain. The Mad Monk needs to complete the task in three days in order to return to Heaven.

programme.title: The Comeback
programme.desc: Uncle Hua is a retired agent who owns an antique shop on an old street. When the old street is forcibly demolished by the local Green Dragon Gang one day, Uncle Huas hidden identity is accidentally revealed, and he is pursued by a mysterious organization headed by Ah Jie. A fatal duel has just begun!

programme.title: Grandmaster, The
programme.desc: Directed by the acclaimed filmmaker Wong Kar Wai, this epic action feature begins in Foshan when Ip Man, the martial arts master from the south, takes up a challenge by ageing northern master Gong Yu Tian. Ip Man wins the fight, but is then defeated by Gong Yu Tians daughter Gong Er, with whom he forms an emotional bond

programme.title: Fall in Love at First Kiss
programme.desc: In this romantic love story starring Taiwanese actors Darren Wang and Jelly Lin, an ordinary girl develops a stubborn crush on the school genius after an unexpected kiss. But with the genius adored by everyone in the school, can their relationship blossom and develop?

programme.title: City of Desire
programme.desc: Sister 13 returns to Macau after 17 years to succeed her fathers underground empire, the prostitution business. She tries to stop their exploitation of the sex workers, but Macaus economy flourished after the handover, propelling the prostitution and gambling businesses. The city is blinded by desire and Sister 13 can do nothing to help

programme.title: Ghost Wife
programme.desc: A high school student gets pregnant and is forced to have an abortion. When she dies from the operation, she returns as a ghost to haunt the apartment complex that she used to live

programme.title: Love · Revolution
programme.desc: Ai Yoshida will do anything for love, including traveling to Thailand with her boyfriend from Japan to run dope. When her boyfriend is kidnapped by the local gangster after a brawl at a bar, Ai sets out on a rescue mission that sends her on an action-packed roller-coaster ride where she meets a professional assassin who breaks out of jail for love.

programme.title: Caught in Time
programme.desc: Based on true events, Detective Zhong Cheng leads a task force in pursuit of Eagle, a criminal gang led by Zhang Sun. Highly methodical and disciplined, the gang manages to avoid capture after each heist. A decade later, the need to stop Eagle is more urgent than ever when Zhong Cheng realizes that his time is almost up to solve the case.

programme.title: Justice Sung Sai Kit
programme.desc: An actor who portrayed the famous Justice Sung Sai Kit is sent back in time to the Qing dynasty after he meets a mysterious woman. There, he reprises his role as a lawyer and sets out to protect the poor from the wealthy. However, as time travelling is outlawed, the time-travel police are on the hunt to stop the duo from changing history.

programme.title: The Lady Improper
programme.desc: Siu Man is divorced by her husband due to her fear of intimacy. After that, she wants to restart her life by taking over her fathers restaurant. Siu Man hires a new chef with unique culinary philosophy that revitalizes her. Tired of the shackles she placed on herself, Siu Man embarks on a journey of self-discovery and sexual liberation.

programme.title: A Cool Fish
programme.desc: In this dark-comedy, cop-turned-security guard Ma faces the ultimate challenge when his boss mysteriously disappears and his paralyzed sister makes a morbid deal with the armed bandits who abduct her.

programme.title: Social Distancing
programme.desc: Cherry is a young girl addicted to the internet. After seeing a warning video about an e-ghost on YouTube, she begins to encounter many mysterious incidents, and the e-ghost also takes control of her family. Cherry must face her unbearable past in order to get out of this horrifying paranormal world...

programme.title: Wo Hu
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police has placed more than a thousand undercover officers in various triad groups to bring down the largest criminal organization in Hong Kong. Betrayal, deceit and murder bring this group of "brothers" into a collision with the law and with each other!

programme.title: Integrity
programme.desc: Anti-corruption senior officer Chen lines up a key witness, corporate accountant Jack, to testify against a tobacco trading company CEO for bribing high-level customs officer as well as smuggling contraband cigarettes. When neither Jack nor the CEO shows up on the day of the hearing, Chen must team up with his ex-wife to launch an investigation.

programme.title: Bangkok Storm
programme.desc: Underground boxer Lin Feng is hunted by the Bangkok triad when he refuses to fight in an illegal match. He escaped successfully but lost his memory. While Feng begins a new life, the triad finds him and hires a top boxer to beat him. As Feng suddenly regains his memory in the process, he vows to take down the triad.

programme.title: Lost Love
programme.desc: Mei tries to get over the death of her young son by becoming a foster parent. For 13 years, Meis dedication to the foster child leads her to neglect her husband and the true needs of the child. It is only through the childs unintentional help that the couple finally manages to salvage their relationship.

programme.title: The Big Sting
programme.desc: Three buddies find a rare artifact known as the Double-Faced God but are poisoned by Lady Wu who steals the treasure from them. Before they die, they get their wives to promise to train their children to take back what is rightfully theirs. These kids grow up to exact a vengeance that turns out to be more hilarious than horrific in this comedy.

programme.title: The Champion
programme.desc: After years in prison, Lu Hu returns home to find himself set up by his ruthless brother Piao, who has taken over the family coal mine business and imprisoned their sister. Hu takes down Piao and saves his sister but their coal mine falls into the hands of a Japanese gang, which Hu and his sister must fight in order to get it back.

programme.title: We Love Millionaires
programme.desc: In this romantic comedy, three beautiful Hong Kong salesgirls travel to Osaka in Japan to pursue their dreams of marrying a rich man. They masquerade as high society debutantes and make their way to a posh resort to meet and woo millionaires (or fake ones!).

programme.title: Duel For Gold
programme.desc: Six swordsmen, including two sisters and their husbands, a ranger and a security man, are trying to steal a million gold taels from the Fu Lai Treasury House, not knowing that one of them is actually an undercover hero. In their quest, they have to double-cross and outwit one another...

programme.title: Double Bliss
programme.desc: Double Bliss tells the story of two students who fall in love and want to wed, but there is one small snag: their parents don't agree! The two ingenious lovebirds come up with what they think is a foolproof plan...They play dead!

programme.title: The Chinese Boxer
programme.desc: A Japanese karate master and Diao Er, who has been expelled from his martial arts school, return to the school to kill the school master and his disciples. After the massacre, disciple Lei Ming embarks on a vigorous training regime and vows to avenge their death. A fatal battle is about to begin

programme.title: The 82 Tenants
programme.desc: Continuing the success of the classic comedy House of 72 tenants, this sequel tells the stories of tenants living in an old building in Hong Kong who are forced to evict by the developers. Some tenants prefer to take the compensation while some resist the move. Will the acquisitions plan destroy the harmony of the neighborhood?

programme.title: The 36Th Chamber Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Gordon Liu plays an anti-Manchu rebel who escapes to the Shaolin Temple and learns what it truly takes to become a martial arts master by challenging the 35 Shaolin Kung Fu chambers, eventually creating the 36th chamber himself.

programme.title: Crazy Shaolin Disciples
programme.desc: Three young kung-fu warriors from wildly different backgrounds become students of Shaolin at the same temple. These three warriors are: Royal Guard Lo Lieh, fleeing soldier, Lo Meng, and villager, Wang Yu.

programme.title: Heroes Two
programme.desc: Shaolin disciple Hung escapes from the burning temple after it is attacked by the Qing army and is badly wounded. He is handed over to the Qing soldiers by Fang as he mistakes Hung for a bandit. When Fang realizes his mistakes, he tries all ways to help Hung escape so that they can team up to fight the Qing army together.

programme.title: Asia-Pol
programme.desc: Asiapol agent Yang Ming Xuan trails a shipment of contraband gold being delivered to gang leader, George Eaton. He enlists the help of a Chinese woman who is trying to avenge her sister and narrowly escapes several deadly traps as he closes in on Eaton's location. This spy film is loosely inspired by the James Bond movies.

programme.title: The Vengeful Beauty
programme.desc: The Flying Guillotine assassins are secretly working for the Emperor and its leader Jin is sent to kill Hon, who knows this secret. Hons pregnant wife Rong seeks to kill Jin but retreats to protect her unborn child. When she is hunted down herself, Rong hooks up with a former Flying Guillotine member and her martial arts senior to fight back...

programme.title: Gossip Street
programme.desc: All neighbours gather to gossip in flat number 8 on the second floor of the Gossip Street apartment building! Most of the residents are common people from all walks of life and there is never a lack of laughter or sarcasm in the neighbourhood. However, when a local mobster wants to change the place into a gambling den, things get serious...

programme.title: Dawn Will Come
programme.desc: Liang Cai drugged the beautiful Qiu Rong and raped her, but promised to marry her after getting his parents consent. Since then, there is no news of his proposal and Qiu Rong confronts Liang Cai when she finds herself pregnant. This is when she discovers that he has already married a rich noble girl and even plans to kill her

programme.title: The Golden Sword
programme.desc: Swordswoman supreme Cheng Pei-pei (Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon) teams up with director/writer/actor Lo Wei (director of Bruce Lee and Jackie Chans first major movies) for an evocative and terrific Martial arts world adventure consisting of a missing blade and a deadly sect of men-hating swordswomen.

programme.title: Hong Kong Nocturne
programme.desc: This joyous, raucous, & colorful tunefest showcases the little seen dancing talents of celebrated kung-fu swordswoman Cheng Pei-Pei, as one of 3 girls dancing their way to the top.

programme.title: The Black Butterfly
programme.desc: Kwan leads a double life as a waitress and as an infamous outlaw skilled in martial arts, The Black Butterfly. When she steals a cache of gold from the Five Devils Rock bandits, she soon has the bandits, and the government, on her tail.

programme.title: The Amorous Lotus Pan
programme.desc: Adapted from the renowned Chinese novel, The Water Margin, this is the story of a poor and beautiful girl Lotus Pan, who is raped by her master and had to be married off to a midget who treats her badly. Lost and lonely, Pan unwittingly becomes a pawn in the game of lust between her husbands playboy brother Wu Song, and a murderous man Men Ching.

programme.title: The Casino
programme.desc: After being separated for many years, two childhood lovers meet in a possibly mythical "Lucky Casino" and vow to rid the establishment of the corrupt military generals, criminals and extortionists!

programme.title: The Dream Of The Red Chamber
programme.desc: Adapted from the great Chinese classic novel of the same name, the son of renowned Jia family, Bao Yu, is deeply in love with his cousin, Dai Yu. However, his mother disapproves of their relationship and plots to arrange Bao Yu to marry another rich girl, resulting in a tragic ending for the perfect couple.

programme.title: Bat Without Wings
programme.desc: The Bat Without Wings, a notorious rapist-murderer, has returned after a five-year absence. A young swordsman and a convoy master investigate the case and suspect that the Bat may be framed. A saying goes that a treasure map is hidden under the Bats knife, so they try to use that to hunt the real culprit

programme.title: The Lark
programme.desc: Sixties pop star Carrie Ku plays the "Little Lark" in this romantic-drama of mistaken identity that is a treasure trove of some of the most popular Mandarin songs of all time.

programme.title: Clan Of Amazons
programme.desc: The martial arts world is plunged into terror when a mysterious figure known as the 'Embroidery Bandit' starts to attack convoys of precious materials. Seemingly unstoppable, the frightened clans decide to call on the expertise of Lu Xiao Feng, an inquisitive fighter and detective to capture the culprit.

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung goes incognito to mix with his people and understand their needs. He encounters many strange things along the way, including being arrested and nearly beheaded. Who will save him?

programme.title: The Daredevils
programme.desc: Corrupt general Wang Li assumes power by killing his superior. The son of the murdered superior befriends four street performers called The Venoms, and they help him take revenge by posing as government officials offering a peace token to the corrupt general. When Wang arrives at a warehouse, he is ambushed by the Venoms!

programme.title: The Three Smiles
programme.desc: A talented scholar, Bo Hu, is attracted by the pretty maid, Qiu Xiang. In order to get close to her and win her love, he disguises as a servant to work in the same household. Qiu Xiang does not believe Bo Hu when he discloses his true identity to her, only falling in love with him when he reveals his talents and with his friends help.

programme.title: The Fantastic Magic Baby
programme.desc: The story is about the legendary Monkey King (Liu Chung-chun) teams up with Goddess of Mercy (Chao Li-chuan) and the Dragon Girl (Lung Nu) to battle the child god Hung Hai-erh (Ting Hua-chung),son of the Ox Demon (Hung Hai-erh) to rescue Tang Tseng, the Holy Pilgrim (Teng Chio-jen).

programme.title: The House Of 72 Tenants
programme.desc: The 72 inhabitants of a dilapidated tenement live under the thumb of a heartless landlady and her sleazy husband. The arrival of a defiant new tenant however, changes their fate. The residents pool their resources together to prevent evictions, deflect targeted harassment by a corrupt policeman and ultimately prevent their home from being sold.

programme.title: The King Boxer
programme.desc: This tale of a honorable fighter's retraining in the "Iron Palm" style, that became the first international martial arts movie hit and made a continent-spanning star of Lo Lieh.

programme.title: The Lotus Lamp
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai plays both mother and son in this lavish fable about a goddess who falls in love with a mortal scholar (Cheng Pei-pei in her debut role). Over two years in production, it was released on the first anniversary of Linda's tragic suicide.

programme.title: My Young Auntie
programme.desc: An elderly landowner marries young Dai Nan to keep his inheritance away from his unscrupulous nephew before he dies. When Dai Nan brings along the deed to meet his other nephew, a series of amusing incidents happen with this young auntie, the nephew and his son. Kara Hui won Best Actress in the first Hong Kong Film Awards for her role as Dai Nan.

programme.title: The Warlord
programme.desc: A bandit became a warlord in northern China by helping Russia fight against Japan. Due to his ignorance and silly behaviour, he is seen as a joke to everyone. The warlord is finally killed by the daughter of a troupe master whom he had killed for no reason, bringing a befitting end to a traitor.

programme.title: The Brave Archer 2
programme.desc: Knowing Guo Jing has won Huang Rongs hand in marriage using the kung fu learned from Jiu Yin manual, Ouyang Feng captures Huang and agrees to release her only if Guo can dictate the content of the manual. Will Guo give in to the threat?

programme.title: The Comedy Of Mismatches
programme.desc: Two pairs of lovers got mismatched accidentally. The man disguises as a woman for his sisters wedding ceremony, while his lover disguises as a man to marry another woman. After the marriage mismatches are revealed, the lovers and their families are taken to court, where Prefecture Chief Qiao manages to work out a happy ending.

programme.title: Angel With The Iron Fists
programme.desc: Lo Wei directs and stars as the chief detective in this gripping thriller; playing alongside Lily Ho, who excels in the role of an undercover avenger that can fight as well as she flirts! Caught between the crime bosses known as Baldhead and Black Widow, she only has four choices: punch, kick, shoot or bombard with explosives!
